<H1>Customising the mail program</H1>

<P>The mail program can be customised by setting variables
in the <SAMP>.mailrc</SAMP> file in your 
<A HREF="../glossary/gh.html#homedir">home directory</A>.</P>

<P>Variables are set using the <STRONG>set</STRONG>
command.  Some variables
have values assigned to them with the  = (equals-sign).</P>

